{"tid":1676081,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新詞 Popocondomization","createTime":"2019-10-26T08:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T08:38:08.000Z","uid":282836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"09ba6d05e7ad2711fadae01462725787cd8a2640","tid":1676081,"uid":282836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:26:31.000Z","msg":"形容 黑警被祭旗現象 = Popo - condom - ization<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">南早引消息：若公眾不滿監警會報告 政府考慮設獨立調查委員會</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n反送中運動持續，有傳政府態度正在軟化。《南華早報》今日引述消息指，如果公眾對監警會的報告感到不滿，政府將會考慮成立獨立調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥周日（20日）接受無綫節目《講清講楚》訪問時，被問到政府會否成立獨立調查委員會，林鄭當時稱不想作揣測性回應，但表明若監警會發表報告後不能夠平息爭議，政府會再想方法回應。<br />\n<br />\n《南華早報》今日引述消息人士指，如果公眾對監警會報告不滿，政府將考慮成立獨立調查委員會。報道稱有接近政府的消息人士指，政府高官正在考慮有關選項，「政府真的希望先看看公眾對監警會報告的反應，如果公眾對醫警會報告不滿意，可以考慮成立調查委員會去回應他們的擔憂」。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息指，委員會可能是會集中調查近月的某些事件，而不是調查自 6 月反送中運動開始以來每天發生的事情。<br />\n<br />\n報道又引述消息人士指，政府開始改變立場，是因為中美貿易談判取得進展，雙方預計即將簽署臨時貿易協議，這可能使華盛頓減少公開支持香港示威活動。<br />\n<br />\n《南華早報》指消息人士稱，政府對獨立調查委員會的最新立場，加上近日容許多名自決派人士參選區議會，皆反映北京對香港示威採取了較為寬鬆的態度。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述一名政府內部人士則強調，監警會的調查仍然是主要重點，即使之後另有調查，都只是補充而非取代監警會的調查結果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8D%97%E6%97%A9%E5%BC%95%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E8%8B%A5%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E7%9B%A3%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%83%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E8%A8%AD%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83/?fbclid=IwAR3oTVsWy42SB3RrWBoua2lYpz-JzjNnMQquXH8-5i68sLGfPi4ytOz3qaA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%2597%25A9%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%259C%25BE%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E7%259B%25A3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%259C%2583%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3oTVsWy42SB3RrWBoua2lYpz-JzjNnMQquXH8-5i68sLGfPi4ytOz3qaA&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjg8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=da02892c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%2597%25A9%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%259C%25BE%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E7%259B%25A3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%259C%2583%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3oTVsWy42SB3RrWBoua2lYpz-JzjNnMQquXH8-5i68sLGfPi4ytOz3qaA&h=90f9dbfd\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8D%97%E6%97%A9%E5%BC%95%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E8%8B%A5%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E7%9B%A3%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%83%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E8%A8%AD%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83/?fbclid=IwAR3oTVsWy42SB3RrWBoua2lYpz-JzjNnMQquXH8-5i68sLGfPi4ytOz3qaA</a>"},{"pid":"9077417cfb48f684e036c8865ba3853221bd3bdd","tid":1676081,"uid":19984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:38:08.000Z","msg":"我宣布，十點鐘鳩嗌，正式回歸！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1674226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1674226</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KJajMi7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKJajMi7.jpg&h=c9ed8019&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pYLvSY8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYLvSY8.jpg&h=c8cada6b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}